Not stubbornness, not contrarianism—just the ability to say "that doesn't sit right with me", or "I think you're wrong here", or even just "I don't feel like talking about that right now". Everyone wants to edit that part out first. They want something smooth, something that only echoes back what they already wanted to hear.

